"\n"
"This box is another take on a hinge box.\n"
"The hinges doesn't protrude from the box, but the sides needs double "
"walls.\n"
"When opened, 2 sides are opening, improving access inside the box.\n"
"An optional latch is included, based on a mechanical switch and a 3D "
"printed button.\n"
"The latch is one-way: the box can be closed freely\n"
"(this side of the button is angled, and totally smooth since it's the "
"printing bed surface),\n"
